{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/game_name-space.png?t=1739109823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A <strong>fast-paced 2D runner</strong> inspired by classic arcade games, offering short yet punishing levels with a focus on <strong>replayability</strong> and <strong>high-score chasing</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Easy to pick up and play, but hard to master</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the game's <strong>chain-based point rewards</strong> by <u>collecting every berry</u>, <u>stomping every enemy</u>, and <u>dodging obstacles at the last possible moment</u>. Only those who push their skills to the limit can achieve the highest scores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/features-space.png?t=1739109823\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A badass goose:</strong> Jump, slide, and hit at just the right moment\u2014sometimes all at once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1739109823\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Master chain-based point multipliers</strong> \u2013 Keep up streaks in every level to maximize your score.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Berry delicious points:</strong> Score by munching on tasty berries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/berries.gif?t=1739109823\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>High-risk, high-reward gameplay:</strong> Earn extra points by flirting with danger\u2014get close to death without dying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/closeCall.gif?t=1739109823\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unleash your fury</strong>: Play aggressively and take down enemies before they strike to rack up even more points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/bees.gif?t=1739109823\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Charming visuals:</strong> Enjoy cute and colorful hand-drawn characters and environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A heartfelt story:</strong> Experience a tale of parental love and delivering justice to those who wronged you\u2014but mostly parental love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/extras/story-intro.gif?t=1739109823\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam achievements:</strong> Take on even greater challenges and show off your skills.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739109823","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/page.bg.jpg?t=1739109823","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/6f9e0b62a2836192784912fac8f549e793b27c65/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739109823","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381470/6f9e0b62a2836192784912fac8f549e793b27c65/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739109823","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3487670,"descriptio